page.title: 12Hobbies and Interests
page.content: I collect key rings.I have a lot of them.My favourite is of a snake a silver one.I also collect stamps.I have a book full of them and I am on my second book.I like to make model aeroplanes I have a lot of them because I have been making them for three years.I also draw but only when I have nothing else to do. I collect thimbles,dolls and books.My favourite thimble is one of Robin Hood.My favourite doll is a Spanish one.My favourite book is called Red Rose.My interests are playing the guitar,reading,running, riding,jogging and playing games.The games I like playing are monopoly, cluedo and hangman. My hobbies are collecting books.I have 150 books by Enid Blyton,Carolyn Keen,Rudyard Kipling,Elinor M.Brent- Dwyer,Malcolm Saville and A.Ransome.
